<strong>Application Instructions:</strong></p>
<p>
Along with your resume submission, please answer the four questions below in your cover letter:</p>
<p>
1. Are you a member of the deviantART community?&nbsp; If yes, what is your username?<br />
2. Name two social networks or blogs sites that you are an active participant on.<br />
3. Explain the difference between Alexa.com and Digg.com.<br />
4. What is your favorite TV show (past or present) and why?</p>
