deviantART, Inc. is looking for a DevOps engineer. This is a remote position and the rest of the DevOps team is remote as well.</p>
<p>
We&#39;re an Alexa top-150 site and have an infrastructure to match that. However, our DevOps team is small. For leverage, we automate as much as possible and build tools when they don&#39;t already exist.</p>
<p>
You&#39;ll be working directly with a few other senior DevOps engineers. You will not have to report to any non-engineer managers.</p>
