Here&#39;s some recent work that DevOps has done:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Began transitioning from ISO-88601 to UTF-8.</li>
<li>
Built a deployment system based on Git, Buildbot, and Puppet.</li>
<li>
Worked with developers to improve database query performance.</li>
<li>
Setup Cacti monitoring for a new service.</li>
<li>
Transitioned some SVN repositories to Git.</li>
<li>
Setup an InnoDB backup system.</li>
<li>
Created a new file storage system for &gt; 1 petabyte of data.</li>
</ul>
<p>
You&#39;re a great fit for us if you:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Have experience with Puppet, Cacti, and/or other cluster management software.</li>
