<li>
Have used compilers/linkers/build tools.</li>
<li>
Know how to use strace, gdb, tcpdump, etc.</li>
<li>
Have compiled your own kernel.</li>
<li>
Have a good sense of humor.</li>
<li>
Are always thinking &quot;What happens if this fails?&quot;.</li>
<li>
Like to document things.</li>
</ul>
